and we're gonna pick one.

508
00:36:37,842 --> 00:36:40,640
That person will be our backup. Okay?

509
00:36:40,845 --> 00:36:42,437
-Sounds fair.
-All right.

510
00:36:42,647 --> 00:36:44,945
