511
00:36:48,419 --> 00:36:50,284
-Pick one.
-Left.

512
00:36:51,155 --> 00:36:53,248
-Thank you.
-You're welcome.

513
00:36:55,493 --> 00:36:57,961
-Ross.
-Joey.

514
00:36:59,998 --> 00:37:02,262
-We should switch.
-Absolutely.

515
00:37:06,137 --> 00:37:09,538
