523
00:37:38,369 --> 00:37:40,132
Or a mustache.

524
00:37:41,439 --> 00:37:44,101
Let's face it. I'm not a kid anymore.

525
00:37:44,309 --> 00:37:47,244
I need someone
who wants the same things.

526
00:37:47,445 --> 00:37:51,905
Coming to my work and telling me
you love me, I want that!

527
00:37:52,450 --> 00:37:56,250
Talking about pig sex over lunch,
I don't want that!

528
00:37:57,522 --> 00:37:59,114
I think that's fair.

529
00:37:59,357 --> 00:38:02,292
Please, don't even talk
to me about fair.

530
00:38:02,427 --> 00:38:05,794
