wanting to marry me then.

531
00:38:05,997 --> 00:38:08,465
Or Chandler wanting to marry me now.

532
00:38:08,666 --> 00:38:11,829
Believe me, nothing
about this is fair. Nothing.

533
00:38:12,003 --> 00:38:14,733
-Nothing! Nothing!
-It's okay.

534
00:38:19,210 --> 00:38:20,609
Nothing.

535
00:38:25,550 --> 00:38:26,744
