573
00:40:52,797 --> 00:40:54,458
No, I don't have a ring.

574
00:41:00,171 --> 00:41:02,196
You go get her, Chandler.

575
00:41:04,742 --> 00:41:07,302
And can I give you a piece of advice?

576
00:41:07,512 --> 00:41:09,377
If you do get her...

577
00:41:10,448 --> 00:41:12,109
...don't let her go.

578
00:41:12,283 --> 00:41:13,750
Trust me.

579
00:41:16,721 --> 00:41:20,179
You know, Richard, you are a good guy.

580
00:41:22,560 --> 00:41:23,686
I know.

581
00:41:24,996 --> 00:41:26,486
I hate that.

582
00:41:41,012 --> 00:41:43,606
-I've gotta find Monica.
-She's gone.

583
00:41:43,981 --> 00:41:47,417
