-I told her everything.

587
00:41:57,795 --> 00:42:02,061
-But she wouldn't believe me.
-Well, where--? Where did she go?

588
00:42:02,266 --> 00:42:07,568
To her parents' . She said you shouldn't
call. But if I were you, I would.

589
00:42:08,105 --> 00:42:12,337
-I can't believe I ruined this.
-I am so sorry, man.

590
00:42:23,554 --> 00:42:26,045
