591
00:42:36,000 --> 00:42:37,490
Oh, my God.

592
00:42:44,041 --> 00:42:45,531
Chandler...

593
00:42:46,878 --> 00:42:48,846
...in all my life...

594
00:42:49,580 --> 00:42:52,242
...I never thought
I would be so lucky...

595
00:42:55,820 --> 00:42:59,415
...as to fall in love with my best....

596
00:43:00,858 --> 00:43:02,348
My best....

597
00:43:03,461 --> 00:43:06,396
There's a reason why
girls don't do this!

598
00:43:07,331 --> 00:43:09,891
I'll do it. I thought....

599
00:43:14,338 --> 00:43:15,965
