602
00:43:27,451 --> 00:43:29,476
Then I realized...

603
00:43:29,854 --> 00:43:32,755
...the only thing that matters
is that you....

604
00:43:36,661 --> 00:43:41,030
You make me happier
than I ever thought I could be.

605
00:43:44,168 --> 00:43:46,068
And if you let me...

606
00:43:46,671 --> 00:43:51,040
...I'll spend all my life trying
to make you feel the same way.

607
00:43:59,951 --> 00:44:01,350
Monica...

608
00:44:03,321 --> 00:44:04,811
...will you marry me?

609
00:44:07,058 --> 00:44:08,548
Yes.

610
00:44:22,540 --> 00:44:25,771
I knew you were likely to take a wife!

611
00:44:27,778 --> 00:44:30,941
Can we come in yet?
We're dying out here!

612
00:44:31,549 --> 00:44:33,073
Come in! Come in!

613
00:44:35,186 --> 00:44:37,017
We're engaged!

614
00:44:43,728 --> 00:44:46,663
This is the least jealous
I've ever been.

615
00:44:47,298 --> 00:44:50,529
Oh, no, wait! This is wrong!
Ross isn't here!

616
00:44:52,536 --> 00:44:56,597
Hell, he's done it three times.
He knows what it's about!

